{"tid":2396359,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國官方公布「15道」藝人禁令　網：不喜歡就「消失」嗎","createTime":"2021-02-05T13:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T19:24:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64133292b44c04e18cf6a03caf25684412d802b5","tid":2396359,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"中國官方公布「15道」藝人禁令　網：不喜歡就「消失」嗎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=893888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D893888&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjN2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=86a952a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D893888&h=27656205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=893888</a><br />\n<br />\n中國演出行業協會5日發布《演出行業演藝人員從業自律管理辦法》新規，一共15條要求藝人應自覺遵守的規範，第1條即明定不得做出「違危害國家統一、主權和領土完整..」，另還有不得「假唱」等。若有違反，將分別施以1年、3年、5年和永久等不同程度的行業聯合抵制。不少網友質疑，這樣的禁令根本沒執行標準「喜歡的就可以，不喜歡的就消失嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n根據《人民日報》報導，該15項規定前三條分別是，不得「違反憲法確定的基本原則，危害國家統一、主權和領土完整，危害國家安全，或者損害國家榮譽和利益」。第二條「煽動民族仇恨、民族歧視，侵害民族風俗習慣，傷害民族感情，破壞民族團結」。第三條「違反國家宗教政策，宣揚邪教、迷信」。<br />\n<br />\n另還有，不得宣揚淫穢、暴力、賭博、毒品等「黑惡勢力非法活動」；危害社會公德或損害民族優秀文化傳統，以及「假唱」、「假演奏等欺騙觀眾」的行為，或違背倫理道德、違反公序良俗等方式進行演出吸引觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n禁令一公布，不少網友直接點名近日引爆「代孕」爭議的藝人鄭爽，認為應該永久抵制。但也有許多網友質疑，禁令的標準在哪裡？沒有標準，靠「網友辦案」嗎？只要喜歡的就可以，不喜歡的就「消失」？<br />\n<br />\n有網友則質疑，這樣的禁令是在為誰的復出開「綠燈」？另有網友提出，一堆出軌的是不是也應該列入。甚至有網友點出，央視帶頭假唱「帳算藝人？還是主辦單位？」"},{"pid":"1b061ad88fe26ca184343f62cdec3f5f1b7970f9","tid":2396359,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"假唱」、「假演奏等欺騙觀眾」的行為  <br />\n呢樣野我又支持"},{"pid":"42525c8980f0d69b6edc68dafdecd213730a5b08","tid":2396359,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://g.udn.com.tw/community/img/PSN_ARTICLE/kalaok/f_4211144_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fcommunity%2Fimg%2FPSN_ARTICLE%2Fkalaok%2Ff_4211144_1.jpg&h=eea443db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實係咪只係想禁呢位中国影帝同佢隻頭馬黑仔強繼續做show咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad95f6e0c5b338193ecb3dccca903a729df27697","tid":2396359,"uid":25758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1b061ad88fe26ca184343f62cdec3f5f1b7970f9","tid":2396359,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"假唱」、「假演奏等欺騙觀眾」的行為  <br />\n呢樣野我又支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"你唱live<br />\n佢播個Mmm<br />\n你就等封殺"},{"pid":"1f60d7f1165d81951623663697d83240830e1920","tid":2396359,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fybncYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfybncYR.jpg&h=2929f567&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c23ef2a622874e6ccfeb3c2a35e85fee1ea77bd","tid":2396359,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">煽動民族仇恨</span><br />\n<br />\n你個政權日日做緊喎，點跟呀？"},{"pid":"976f51140fec8682828d561d19c4bb06552a7faa","tid":2396359,"uid":321002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"曾志偉，陳小春直播賣假野，係咪應該一世黑名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc7f687f86de14c01884f26bfed11ee2921d3b6","tid":2396359,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"這就是中蟈，第一天出生嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5d6e2e214a82abf17b4e6225d8e0895ea47706","tid":2396359,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"976f51140fec8682828d561d19c4bb06552a7fa